race.comment: SATIN STILETTO (7) progressing nicely and set to peak for this. Came out quickly from the wide gate with a fighting on-pace third over 1200m at this track second-up. Gets the same set-up today and expected to go close. MICRO MIKKI (15) two runs back have been solid and has the ability to win in town. Savaged the line when fourth over 1200m here in this class. Was a month between runs on that occasion and a top-three finish is on the cards. KINGDOM UNDERSIEGE (10) talented gelding undefeated in two runs back. Deserves his shot in town after returning a career peak with a slick win over 1200m at Lismore. The booking of Rawiller is a good lead from the low gate. CRUSADER KINGS (4) on the up and ready for this trip.
